title: Police: Men defied stay-at-home order outside women's clinic
description: GREENSBORO, N.C. (AP) — Seven people have been charged with violating stay-at-home orders while protesting Monday outside an abortion clinic in Greensboro, authorities said.
content:
GREENSBORO, N.C. (AP) Seven people have been charged with violating stay-at-home orders while protesting Monday outside an abortion clinic in Greensboro, authorities said.
